TableColumns.Name: FlipDescription
TableColumns.Formula: IF(FlipFromName=Name,"No Movement", CONCATENATE("From ", FlipFromName," to ", Name))

TableColumns.Name: Description
TableColumns.Formula: IF(CustomDescription=BLANK(),CONCATENATE('Rotate 3x3 "board" 90 degrees ', IF(IsClockwise, "RIGHT-hand (Clockwise)","LEFT-hand (Counter-Clockwise)")," around the middle cell"),CustomDescription)
